        "text": "Between him",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The Revised Version reads \"himself,\" which is the evident meaning. The parallel leaves out, however, mention of Jehoiada as party to the covenant, viewing him rather as ",
