    "name": "Keil and Delitzsch Biblical Commentary on the Old Testament",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "The renewal of the covenant, extirpation of Baal-worship, and the solemn entry of the king into his palace, as in ",
